Content:
I just watched a live stream and kmd was brought up. The take was not a positive one but an important one to see as we go forward. The take was: Why would I buy kmd when it literally has done nothing as far as price action in over a year? Sure they’re “developing” but another 5 teams will pop up with marketing and just take the work they’ve done and put it to use. 
On top of that, there are so many bagholders that this won’t have a chance to grow as everyone has been underwater for so long, they will dump the first sign of breakeven or profit.

@jl777c there really needs to be a marketing effort here man. I appreciate the work you all put into this, but without a solid marketing effort all you are doing is paving the road for someone else to surpass you.
